* A set of constants for implementing a time zone data content provider, which is used by the time
 * zone updater application.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: AUTHORITY
variables.comment: * The authority that must be used for the time zone data content provider. * To be accepted by the time zone updater application it must be exposed by the * package specified in the config_timeZoneRulesDataPackage config value.

variables.name: AUTHORITY_URI
variables.comment: A content:// style uri to the authority for the time zone data content provider
